quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  43,26,"Janto tuma Ibraahiima maakannoo ben makko e yim…ďe makko …ďen: \"Min on ko mi da…óndii…óo e kon ko rewoton"
  43,27,"si wanaa On tagu…óo lam, Kanko On, O fewnay lam"
  43,28,"O wa…ói ngol konngol heddotoongol …ďaawo makko, belajo'o, …ďe ruttoto"
  43,29,"Si ko woni, Mi dakmitii …ďee …óoo e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, haa nde goonga kan arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, e Nulaa…óo …ďanngu…óo"
  43,30,"Nde goonga kan arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'i: \"∆äum ko mbilewu, menen ko men yeddu…ďe …óum"
  43,31,"∆Āe wi'iti: \"Ko hanno ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinee e gorko maw…óo ca'e …óen …ói…ói"
  43,32,"E ko kam…ďe senndata yurmeende Joomi maa nden? Awa ko Menen woni ko senndi nguureeji ma…ď…ďe …óin hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ka nguurndam aduna. Men …ďamti yoga ma…ď…ďe e hoore …ďeya, darjaaji, fii no yoga ma…ď…ďe jogitora yoga eeltane. Haray ko yurmeende Joomi maa nden, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e kon ko …ďe moo…ďata"
  43,33,"Si wanaano fii wata yim…ďe …ďen wonu mofte goote, Men wa…óayno e cuu…ói kala yeddu…óo Hinnaranke On: ki…ď…ďe kaalisi e Ňčabbir…óe ka …ďe ∆īawra"
  43,34,"(Men wa…óayno kadi) e cuu…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, dame e nda…ó…óude ka …ďe so…ď…ďindoo"
  43,35,"e cu…óaari. Kono …óum fow wonaali, si wanaa dakamme nguurndam aduna. Ko laakara on ka Joomi maa, woni fii gom…óum…ďe …ďen"